== Festivals ==
* Setsubun Festival – February 3
* Rakugo performance event

== Access ==
It is a 5‑minute walk from {{ill|JR East|ja|JR東日本|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Tobu Railway|ja|東武鉄道|12=draft|12=draft}}’s {{ill|Kashiwa Station|ja|柏駅|12=draft|12=draft}}.

